		Bugfix

	* bblog/bBlog_plugins/function.getrecentposts.php 1.7:
		use TRUE instead of 'yes'
		This allows you to use :
		{if $post.newday}<h3>{$post.posttime|date_modifier:jim}</h3>{/if}
		in your index template, to get a h3 title if the posts are from a new day..

