2003-06-18	revjim
	* bblog/bBlog_plugins/function.getrecentposts.php 1.3:
		Made the check for the section parameter more specific.

	* bblog/bBlog_plugins/block.comments.php 1.2:
	* bblog/inc/bBlog.class.php 1.4:
		Moved model functions outside of block.comments.php and into bBlog.class where
		they belong. This will allow other plugins to use the comments API.

	* bblog/bBlog_plugins/function.getposts.php 1.1:
		Initial commit of getposts function. For use in retrieving a 
		list of posts or a single post.

	* bblog/bBlog_plugins/function.getrecentposts.php 1.1:
		Inital import of getrecentposts function.

	* bblog/inc/bBlog.class.php 1.5:
		Fixed a few typos. Added back in preformatted HTML values for 
		website, email, replylink and permalink.

	* bblog/bBlog_plugins/function.getpost.php 1.1:
		Initial commit of getpost function.

	* bblog/inc/bBlog.class.php 1.3:
		Annotated Section Code modifications found in previous commit.

	* bblog/bBlog_plugins/function.getposts.php 1.2:
		This function is better implemented as two functions. Removing.

	* bblog/bBlog_plugins/block.comments.php 1.3:
		Fixed a few typos due to moving the functions into the bBlog 
		class.

	* bblog/inc/bBlog.class.php 1.2:
		Added "commentcount" to post array.

	* bblog/bBlog_plugins/function.getpost.php 1.2:
	* bblog/bBlog_plugins/function.getrecentposts.php 1.2:
		Apparently, this version of smarty doesn't do auto assignment with the assign parameter.
		This also means that anything returned is outputted to the view.
		All return calls have been modified to return nothing.

	* bblog/inc/bBlog.class.php 1.6:
		Corrected a few more typos due to the moved functions.

